These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, chinese, mexican
1. the mexican is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the mexican is between the nigerian and the chinese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, crime, thriller
1. the person watching western movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | western | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, dubstep, rock
1. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of pop and the fan of rock##2
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | dubstep | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | frog | lizard | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, almond-milk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | sprite | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
